          <source>The example then sets the <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.DataContext%2A&gt;</ph> property of the <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.ListBox&gt;</ph> to the <ph id="ph3">`DataSet`</ph> object.</source>
        </trans-unit>
